page.title: 11Population
page.content: The{population}of this area has changed greatly over the last twenty-five years with a gradual {influx}of people from other counties, especially London and the Home Counties. The family which is born and bred in this locality is a rarity these days as are familiar faces that one used to recognise and converse with every day. The{changing}population is steadily on the increase with new houses being built on a small scale,varied types of employment plays a part in this structure. The{traditional}inhabitants are adversed to movement and change even to the extent of taking their holidays on the Norfolk coast.
